The '''Research Institute for Nature and Forest''' ('''INBO''') ([[Dutch language|Dutch]]: Instituut voor Natuur- en Bosonderzoek) is a scientific institute in [[Belgium]]. It was established from the merger of the [[Institute for Forestry and Game Management]] and the [[Institute of Nature Conservation]] on January 1, 2006.

